  "texts": [
    "Indeed, in the bound on the ERM, λ is chosen to minimize the bound, but the estimation procedure is not affected by λ.",
    "The bound for the Gibbs posterior is also minimized with respect to λ, but ρλ depends on λ.",
    "So, if you make a mistake when choosing λ, this will have bad consequences not only on the bound, but also on the practical performances of the method.",
    "This means also that if the bound is not tight, it is likely that the λ obtained by minimizing the bound will not lead to good performances in practice.",
    "(We present in Section 3 bounds that do not depend on a parameter like λ)."
  ],
